text: Kalraj Mishra (born 1 July 1941) is an Indian politician. In September 2019, he became the Governor of Rajasthan. Briefly in 2019, he was Governor of Himachal Pradesh. He also was a Cabinet Minister of Micro, Small and Medium Enterprises. He was a member of Parliament from Deoria constituency in Uttar Pradesh from 2014 to 2019. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Governors of Himachal Pradesh Category:Governors of Rajasthan Category:Members of the Lok Sabha Category:Members of the Rajya Sabha
